      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BALMORAL QUEEN (1) is in hot form with back to back wins at this track, running a scintillating 18.45 two back following up with 18.52 last time. Can continue winning form here if runs up to time two back. DARCY MAC (3) ran below best last time finishing fifth (19.19) over 330m at this track in a Grade 5. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won six of 12 tries. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Shapes as one to consider. TINY BIANCA (2) is in consistent form, jumping from this same box when a 6 length third in a Mix 1/2/3 at this track and making it back to back minors. Safe beginner and drawn well close to the inside. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. POLKA DOT PINK (7) is another with top-three prospects.",
